rows.label: qst710803_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey! Never expected to meet someone
else up here!

rows.label: qst710803_msg0002
rows.name:
You here to fish too?
Well, it's my first time up here too...

rows.label: qst710803_msg0004
rows.name:
Chiko said I'd gone missing and
sent you to look for me?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0005
rows.name:
Hahaha, "gone missing"!
That's completely over the top!

rows.label: qst710803_msg0006
rows.name:
I've just come up here to try and catch
some fish to replace the ones we lost
in Iira.

rows.label: qst710803_msg0007
rows.name:
What! The fish are back to normal?
Ah, Tyler had you sort it out?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0009
rows.name:
Did you say my wife, Chiko, had
sent you?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0011
rows.name: Gulp! My wife...is she...in good spirits?

rows.label: qst710803_msg0013
rows.name:
An anger worse than the Grail could
ever muster...

rows.label: qst710803_msg0014
rows.name:
I-I-I better go!
Thanks for telling me!
